title: Bob Dylan Albumliveseries Volume 1
description:
The idea of the albumliveseries is to provide a compilation of the songs from the studioalbums played live. 
Each song has one example which has been chosing for that it is rare or special or excellent performed. 
The songperformances go from the sixties until 2006. 
Part I of the album live series has the songs from the studioalbums Bob Dylan The Freewheelin? ,Another Side of Bob Dylan, The times they are a changin?, Bringing it all back home Highway 61 on them. 
Production www.dylannl.blogspot.com artwork Noirdesir france
